{"id": "1341771957410070629", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "珊算獨立體系，沒超限請自動退出，不然沒啥用(跳過\n米粒要2啟跳過\n凱克斯你沒練跳過\n水母最好有3啟但2啟我覺得OK\n其他角都能用\n結\n鯊圖希萊墨\n水母圖墨法\n鯊凱圖希等你凱2啟(凱值得抽", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T14:02:43.564000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1341774930567630959", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "渾沌\n塔維請去搞2啟(大給的牌有預備)，不然不好用，所以我先不考慮\n寧不會用\n諾、艾可以湊低配盾擊(你沒練跳過\n\n24->百搭角\n莉莉最重要是2、3啟(\n萊克看你要不要補1啟\n哈姆0啟能用(一般會到2啟\n# 加侖、4隻SR角都要練\n結\n24哈萊 + ?", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T14:14:32.420000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
